ActExpropriation Act
SubjectOrder Directing the Expropriation of the Lac-Mégantic Rail Bypass Project
PrecisOrder directing that there be substituted for the 90 days referred to in paragraph 19(1)(c) of the Act a period of 46 days in order to grant early physical possession of the lands expropriated by the Minister of Public Services and Procurement for the LAC-MÉGANTIC RAIL BYPASS PROJECT to avoid construction delays.
